name: Aged care
discribtion: We lead the way in aged care, providing specialised medical care for people over 65 years for issues including dementia, falls, continence problems and rheumatology.

name: Diagnosis & investigation
discription: Diagnosing medical issues early is crucial. Whatever your condition, we can diagnose it using a range of technologies and pathologies.

name: Medical &Surgical
discription: We have the most comprehensive medical services in the state, with expert care covering a wide range of illnesses plus emergency and elective surgery, ensuring our community receives the care they need.

name: Rehabilitation
discription: We are a statewide provider of rehabilitation services, helping people after accident or illness to regain function, independence and wellbeing.

name: Mental Health
discription: We provide a range of specialised mental health services for people of all ages in our community.

name: Emergency, trauma & intensive care
discription: Well known for being a major trauma service, we run two very busy emergency departments and have one of the largest Intensive Care Units, offering the best care in the country.
